structure.name: UBX-ESF-MEAS
structure.description: External sensor fusion measurements. Contains sensor measurements with timestamp. Optionally, can include timestamp that the message was received at the receiver. Multiple measurements can be included in a single message (1 measurement per sensor type). An optional calibration time tag (4 bytes, 'ms' unit) is present if the `calibTtagValid` bit in the `flags` field is set, following the repeated data groups.
